snippet.title: Budget Cuts Ultimate - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Budget Cuts Ultimate will be available on PS VR2 and Meta Quest 2 on June 1, 2023. Make your escape in this launch trailer for Budget Cuts Ultimate, the VR stealth action gaming experience that combines the complete Budget Cuts 1 and Budget Cuts 2 games into one adventure.

In Budget Cuts Ultimate, you must zip, sneak, and stab your way through enemy-filled offices, trains, warehouses, and skyscrapers to take down the evil cost-cutting robots at TransCorp. Is humanity being optimized out of existence altogether?

#GameTrailers #VR #Gaming
